[00:13:42.391] Browser LOG     {"content":"At New Purpose House, we believe every woman deserves the chance to heal, rebuild, and create a new path forward. This application is the first step in joining our supportive community. Our 24-month program is designed to provide structure, stability, and the tools needed for long-term success. We ask these questions to better understand your background and how we can serve you best. All information you provide will remain confidential and used only to determine program eligibility. Take your time, answer honestly, and know that by applying today, you are choosing hope, healing, and a new purpose for your life.","notice":"New Purpose House – Application for Services. Please complete the form below to apply for residency and support services at New Purpose House. All information will be kept confidential.","title":"Begin Your Journey with New Purpose House"}
[00:13:42.391] Browser LOG     {"content":"At New Purpose House, we believe every woman deserves the chance to heal, rebuild, and create a new path forward. This application is the first step in joining our supportive community. Our 24-month program is designed to provide structure, stability, and the tools needed for long-term success. We ask these questions to better understand your background and how we can serve you best. All information you provide will remain confidential and used only to determine program eligibility. Take your time, answer honestly, and know that by applying today, you are choosing hope, healing, and a new purpose for your life.","notice":"New Purpose House – Application for Services. Please complete the form below to apply for residency and support services at New Purpose House. All information will be kept confidential.","title":"Begin Your Journey with New Purpose House"}
